data.description: Are You Looking For A Spacious Home On A Corner Lot That Has Been Completely Renovated Down To The Studs? This 1800+ Sqft, 4bed/2 Full Bath Home Is Move-in Ready!! Featuring Brand New Flooring Throughout The Entire Home, New Cabinetry In The Kitchen And Bathrooms. With A Yard Big Enough To Entertain Everyone And A Huge 2+ Car Extended Garage To Store All Your Toys. New Windows, New Central A/c, New Hot Water Heater, New Water Softener, & More! Everything Is Brand New! This Property Won't Last Long, Schedule Your Showing Today! Available For Showings Starting June 23rd!
